Package: rainfarmr
Title: Stochastic precipitation downscaling with the RainFARM method
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Jost", "von Hardenberg", email = "j.vonhardenberg@isac.cnr.it",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: R package implementing the RainFARM (Rainfall Filtered Autoregressive Model) stochastic precipitation downscaling method. Adapted for climate downscaling according to (D'Onofrio et al. 2018) and with fine-scale orographic weights (Terzago et al. 2018).
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
License: Apache License 2.0
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Encoding: UTF-8
